manassakshi ( kannada : ಮನಸ ಸಾಕ ಷಿ ) is a 1968 indian kannada film , directed by s. k. a. chari and produced by a l srinivasan .   the film stars rajkumar , bharathi , narasimharaju and m. p. shankar in lead roles .   the film had musical score by g. k. venkatesh .   the movie was a remake of 1961 tamil movie thirudadhe .